OL,3,CEntering football match without a
OL,4,Cticket to become criminal offence
OL,6,FEntering a football match without a
OL,7,Fticket will become a criminal offence
OL,8,Fahead of Sunday's Carabao Cup final at
OL,9,FWembley, more than five years after
OL,10,Fthousands of ticketless fans stormed
OL,11,Fthe same stadium.
OL,13,FOffenders across England and Wales
OL,14,Fwill face a five-year, football
OL,15,Fbanning order as well as a fine of up
OL,16,Fto #1,000 from the weekend onwards.
OL,18,FLives were put at risk when supporters
OL,19,Fbroke into Wembley Stadium at the Euro
OL,20,F2020 final, a subsequent review by
OL,21,FBaroness Louise Casey found.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
