PN,30702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774015869
OL,3,CEntering football match without a
OL,4,Cticket to become criminal offence
OL,6,FThe new laws follow her findings that
OL,7,Fsanctions on breaking into stadiums
OL,8,Fwere weak and that tailgating should
OL,9,Fbecome a criminal offence.
OL,11,FPolicing minister Sarah Jones said:
OL,12,F"This is a new piece of legislation
OL,13,Fand, of course, the police are
OL,14,Fplanning on how to implement it."
OL,16,FIt gives officers "more armoury" to
OL,17,F"deter and then respond to people who
OL,18,Fare disrespecting paying fans by
OL,19,Ftrying to get in without paying
OL,20,Fthemselves".
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@aO]xD@SOUxD@`O]yD@AOU|D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
