CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774015869
OL,3,CEntering football match without a
OL,4,Cticket to become criminal offence
OL,6,FShe added: "This is something that I
OL,7,Fdon't think any party could oppose `
OL,8,Fit cannot be right that some people
OL,9,Fpay and some people don't and that
OL,10,Fpeople are put at risk, in danger,
OL,11,Fwhen people are tailgating.
OL,13,F"So we need there to be an appropriate
OL,14,Fresponse and a #1,000 fine or five-
OL,15,Fyear football banning order I think
OL,16,Fwill be a great deterrent."
OL,26,@nD@LOUuD@AOUxD@[O]
