OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774015869
OL,3,CEntering football match without a
OL,4,Cticket to become criminal offence
OL,6,FTailgating is when fans get through
OL,7,Fstadium turnstiles by walking closely
OL,8,Fbehind ticket holders. There was
OL,9,Fpreviously no specific legal penalties
OL,10,Ffor attending a football game without
OL,11,Fa ticket.
OL,13,FThe Unauthorised Entry to Football
OL,14,FMatches Act will also make it illegal
OL,15,Fto knowingly try to enter a match with
OL,16,Fforged tickets, passes and
OL,17,Faccreditation documents, as well as by
OL,18,Fpretending to be a member of stadium
OL,19,For playing staff.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
