OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774015869
OL,3,CEntering football match without a
OL,4,Cticket to become criminal offence
OL,6,FIt follows an independent review of
OL,7,Fthe Uefa European Championship final
OL,8,Fheld at Wembley in north London on
OL,9,FJuly 11 2021.
OL,11,FBaroness Casey identified more than 20
OL,12,F"near misses" that could have resulted
OL,13,Fin serious injury or death as a result
OL,14,Fof ticketless individuals trying to
OL,15,Fgain entry, and in some cases
OL,16,Fsucceeding, for the England v Italy
OL,17,Fmatch.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
