OL,3,CEntering football match without a
OL,4,Cticket to become criminal offence
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FAround 100,000 people travelled to
OL,12,FWembley for the final "of which
OL,13,Fapproximately 2,000 gained entry to
OL,14,Fthe stadium without tickets", with 17
OL,15,Fmass breaches of the gates in the 90
OL,16,Fminutes before kick-off until the
OL,17,Fpenalty shootout.
OL,26,@tD@WOUvD@\O]
