CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774015869
OL,3,CEntering football match without a
OL,4,Cticket to become criminal offence
OL,6,FThe new laws also come after problems
OL,7,Fencountered by Liverpool supporters
OL,8,Fduring their Champions League final
OL,9,Fagainst Real Madrid in Paris in 2022.
OL,11,FIn that instance, authorities were
OL,12,Ffound to be at fault for major
OL,13,Fproblems around the Stade de France
OL,14,Fdespite their attempts to pin the
OL,15,Fblame on Liverpool supporters.
OL,17,FSeveral fans were denied entry despite
OL,18,Fhaving legitimate tickets for the
OL,19,Fmatch, while police also used pepper
OL,20,Fspray and tear gas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
